t and operations prior to ttm mr murphy worked at db zwirn  co as a vice president with oversight of all asset management functions for the assets group where he managed credit reporting and credit administration and led the workout management for “problem” assets for the assets group prior to d b zwirn mr murphy was at hudson castle group formerly ibex capital markets an independent structured finance advisory company specializing in the management of assetbacked lending vehicles where he was responsible for all aspects of conduit operations treasury and credit administration for five asset backed commercial paper conduits with commitments in excess of  billion mr murphy holds a mbs graduate school of business and a bcomm in accounting both from university college dublin ireland and earned the chartered financial analyst designation murphyatalayacapcom sachin u sarnobat managing director managing director prior to joining atalaya mr sarnobat worked with prospect capital management a multibillion dollar credit and private equity fund where he served on the investment committee headed the illiquid public debt strategy and structured private investments in esoteric assets prior to prospect capital management mr sarnobat also worked in the investment banking practices of citigroup and merrill lynch where he originated and executed mergers acquisitions debt and equity transactions for a variety of private equity and corporate clients mr sarnobat began his career at a technology startup that provided advanced analytics to the consumer credit risk industry and was awarded a us patent related to data mining mr sarnobat earned his bs in chemical engineering from the university of mumbai and his mba with honors from columbia university business school mr sarnobat also earned his masters in chemical engineering from the university of tennessee knoxville based on his research on chaos theory at oak ridge national laboratory sarnobatatalayacapcom matthew h spiro managing direct